@startuml svc-scheduling-orchestrator--get-schedule-optimization

!include ../theme.puml
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #2563eb
}

header [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/#integration-context ⬆ svc-scheduling-orchestrator Integration Context]]

title GET /schedule-optimization\nGet schedule optimization recommendations\n<size:10><color:#7c3aed>ARCHITECT OVERRIDE — enriched with constraint-solving and capacity logic</color></size>

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-scheduling-orchestrator" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/]] #DBEAFE
participant "Guide Mgmt" as GM [[/microservices/svc-guide-management/]] #E0E7FF
participant "Location Svc" as LS [[/microservices/svc-location-services/]] #F1F5F9
participant "Trip Catalog" as TC [[/microservices/svc-trip-catalog/]] #FEF3C7
participant "Analytics" as AN [[/microservices/svc-analytics/]] #F1F5F9
database "PG + Valkey" as DB [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-scheduling-orchestrator.html View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : GET /schedule-optimization
activate GW #2563eb
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #2563eb

note right of Svc : Load current day schedule\nIdentify optimization targets:\n- Unassigned trips\n- Overloaded guides\n- Capacity violations

== Data Collection ==

Svc -> GM : [[/microservices/svc-guide-management/#get-guidesavailable-list-available-guides GET /guides/available]]
activate GM #E0E7FF
GM --> Svc : All available guides\n(skills, current load, location)
deactivate GM

Svc -> LS : [[/microservices/svc-location-services/#get-locationslocation_id-get-location-details GET /locations/{id}/capacity]]
activate LS #F1F5F9
LS --> Svc : Location capacities\n(max_groups, current_occupancy)
deactivate LS

Svc -> TC : [[/microservices/svc-trip-catalog/#get-tripstrip_id-get-trip-details GET /trips/{trip_id}]]
activate TC #FEF3C7
TC --> Svc : Trip requirements\n(guide certifications needed,\nmin/max group sizes)
deactivate TC

== Constraint Solving ==

note right of Svc : Optimization algorithm:\n1. Score each guide-trip pairing\n   (certification match × proximity\n    × workload balance)\n2. Apply hard constraints:\n   - Location capacity limits\n   - Guide certification requirements\n   - Rest period minimums (8h)\n3. Apply soft constraints:\n   - Guest language preferences\n   - Guide trail familiarity\n4. Select optimal assignment

alt Feasible solution found
    note right of Svc #D1FAE5 : Apply optimized assignments\nto schedule
else Infeasible — capacity exceeded
    note right of Svc #FEF3C7 : Return partial solution\nwith unassignable trips flagged\nfor manual resolution
end

== Update Schedule ==

Svc -> DB : UPDATE daily_schedules\nSET assignments = optimized_result,\noptimization_score, optimized_at
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Updated
deactivate DB

== Async Metrics ==

Svc ->> AN : [[/microservices/svc-analytics/#post-events-ingest-analytics-event Log optimization metrics]]\n(score_before, score_after,\nunassigned_count, duration_ms)

Svc --> GW : 200 OK\n(optimization_score,\nassignments_changed,\nunresolved_conflicts)
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 200 OK
deactivate GW

@enduml
